headline: J.B. Hunt eyes intermodal pricing inflection
summary: J.B. Hunt Transport Services is hopeful that Western rail service will improve, allowing it to layer higher contract pricing across record intermodal volumes. The post J.B. Hunt eyes intermodal pricing inflection appeared first on FreightWaves.
